## Volume Controls ##
# Increase volume
"amixer set Master playback 5+"
    m:0x0 + c:123
    XF86AudioRaiseVolume

# Decrease volume
"amixer set Master playback 5-"
    m:0x0 + c:122
    XF86AudioLowerVolume

# Mute volume
"amixer set Master toggle"
   XF86AudioMute

